headline: Realty Income: Attractive For Income Investors, But Mr. Market May Be Trying To Tell Us Something (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Realty Income offers stable income and solid dividends, but modest growth, tenant risks, and underperformance cloud its outlook. See why O stock is downgraded to hold.

headline: REIT Stocks Have Struggled. Where Income Investors Can Find Value.
summary: Real estate investment trust shares have been hit by still-high interest rates and strong stock sectors. But disparities are wide, and sectors such as healthcare and retail remain strong.
